<br />
<pre><code data-type="">Foo foo = null;
foor = bar;</code></pre><br />
<br />
2. 擺哂所有野落Map/Dictionary, 再pass黎pass去,每次用都拎番出黎再擺番落去 e.g.<br />
<br />
<pre><code data-type="">...
public Map foo(Map bar) {
	String foo1 = bar.get(&quot;bar1&quot;) == null ? bar.get(&quot;bar1&quot;) : &quot;&quot;;
	String foo2 = bar.get(&quot;bar2&quot;) == null ? bar.get(&quot;bar2&quot;) : &quot;&quot;;
	String foo3 = bar.get(&quot;bar3&quot;) == null ? bar.get(&quot;bar3&quot;) : &quot;&quot;;
	....

	bar.put(&quot;bar1&quot;, &quot;foo1&quot;);
	bar.put(&quot;bar2&quot;, &quot;foo2&quot;);
	bar.put(&quot;bar3&quot;, &quot;foo3&quot;);
	....

	return bar;
}


...
Map bar = new&lt;&gt;();
bar.put(&quot;bar1&quot;, &quot;foo1&quot;);
bar.put(&quot;bar2&quot;, &quot;foo2&quot;);
bar.put(&quot;bar3&quot;, &quot;foo3&quot;);
...

foo1(bar);
foo2(bar);
foo3(bar);
foo4(bar);
foo5(bar);
foo6(bar);
...
</code></pre><br />
<br />
3. 整一個god object, 成個application再pass黎pass去,好多地方都用緊, 每個method都pass依個object, 但好多時只係用其中一D member variables, 完全睇唔到邊樣野幾時有用緊幾時無用<br />
<br />
4. 無限utilities classes, business logic都係d CommonUtils入面<br />
<br />
5. 一個jar一個package, 入面一個class有幾百個methods<br />
<br />
6. 個comment唔係我加既<br />
